edu.rpi.phil.legup
Class TransitionCell

java.lang.Object
  edu.rpi.phil.legup.TransitionCell
public class TransitionCell
extends java.lang.Object

A single cell change that should occur when transitioning from one state to the next. The transition that this should be applied to is determined by the transition branch number.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Drew Housten
